quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,1,"O you enveloped in your cloak!"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,2,"Arise, and warn,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,3,"and magnify the glory of your Lord,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,4,"and purify your robes,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,5,"and shun uncleanness,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,6,"and bestow not favour in order to seek from others a greater return,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,7,"and persevere for your Lord's sake."{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,8,"When the Trumpet shall be sounded,"
  74,9,"that will surely be a hard day,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  74,10,"not an easy day for the unbelievers."{1},footnotes:1:1